{"data":[{"date":"07:17 08/08","title":"Sarri h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ed9i thu cho Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/sarri-hua-hen-ngay-cuoi-chuyen-nhuong-boi-thu-cho-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea. T\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia c\u1ee7a The Blues chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n tinh th\u1ea7n cho m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 Courtois v\u00e0 Kepa</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 tin \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Kepa Arrizabalaga tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Athletic Bilbao. The Blues \u0111ang ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edbm \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ea1n ch\u00f3t c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i m\u1ea1nh tay c\u1ee7a Chelsea sau khi Thibaut Courtois quy\u1ebft ch\u00ed t\u1edbi Real Madrid. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf 2 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a The Blues b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n ngh\u1ec9 ph\u00e9p. Bi\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Courtois, Chelsea quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi d\u00e0nh cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n v\u1edbi Kepa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/Maurizio-Sarri-phat-bieu-ve-chuyen-nhuong-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kepa Arrizabalaga \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n Chelsea</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean sau khi Chelsea v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Lyon tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup (h\u00f2a 0-0 sau 2 hi\u1ec7p ch\u00ednh), HLV Maurizio Sarri th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1ea5t m\u1ebfn m\u1ed9 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Kepa: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Kepa 1 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f2n \u1edf Napoli v\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n gi\u1ecfi d\u00f9 c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, Sarri mi\u1ec5n c\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Courtois. &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5. T\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Lyon. Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft g\u00ec v\u1ec1 Courtois. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi CLB c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Sau \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Sarri\" title=\"HLV Sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/hlv-maurizio-sarri-du-am-tran-chelsea-vs-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 ng\u00e0y 9/8 (h\u1ea1n ch\u00f3t mua s\u1eafm t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh) b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n. &ldquo;T\u00f4i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y r\u1ea5t b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y&rdquo;, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Kepa, nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 quan tr\u1ecdng kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Chelsea l\u00e0 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Eden Hazard. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb Real Madrid ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o t\u1eeb gi\u1edd cho t\u1edbi khi k\u1ef3 mua s\u1eafm m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-muon-kovacic-172-193958.html\">L\u1ed9 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a Mateo Kovacic \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-cho-nantes-muon-matt-miazga-172-193916.html\">Sao tr\u1ebb Chelsea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/courtois-tu-choi-tro-lai-chelsea-quyet-tam-den-real-bang-duoc-172-193892.html\">Courtois t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Real b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-chelsea-courtois-va-hazard-cu-thoai-mai-ra-di-172-193879.html\">Sao Chelsea: &ldquo;Courtois v\u00e0 Hazard c\u1ee9 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i ra \u0111i&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/willian-chinh-thuc-dua-ra-cau-tra-loi-cho-mu-barca-172-193877.html\">Willian ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho M.U, Barca</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2117","checkdouble":"193991"},{"date":"07:28 08/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 8/8: Pogba n\u1eb1ng n\u1eb7c \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/3/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-88-pogba-nang-nac-doi-roi-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 8/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Everton mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n Zouma c\u1ee7a Chelsea. </strong>Everton \u0111ang t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Kurt Zouma c\u1ee7a Chelsea. The Toffees \u0111\u00e3 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Marcos Rojo c\u1ee7a Manchester United v\u00e0 Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barcelona song t\u1edbi nay ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Pogba n\u1eb1ng n\u1eb7c \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi M.U. </strong>Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Ed Woodward c\u1ee7a Man United r\u1eb1ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Barcelona. Theo t\u1edd Daily Mail, anh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd c\u00e1c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Barca theo giao k\u00e8o c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 5 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 88 Pogba n\u1eb1ng n\u1eb7c \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 88 Pogba n\u1eb1ng n\u1eb7c \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/Tien-ve-Paul-Pogba-tro-lai-MU-sau-ky-nghi-he-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pogba kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Milan \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Bakayoko. </strong>AC Milan \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Tiemoue Bakayoko t\u1eeb Chelsea. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt trong vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 \u1edf Monaco. Anh hi\u1ec7n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng HLV Maurizio Sarri b\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nCandreva t\u00ednh chuy\u1ec7n r\u1eddi Inter.</strong> Antonio Candreva \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Inter Milan. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh 31 tu\u1ed5i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb Monaco. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng Keita Balde \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Lazio.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nTottenham ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch sao tr\u1ebb Anh 7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. </strong>Theo th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a BBC, Aston Villa v\u00e0 Tottenham ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1ch nhau 7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jack Grealish. Spurs hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 t\u1ea1i Anh kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00eam 9/8 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jack Grealish cua Aston Villa\" title=\"Jack Grealish cua Aston Villa\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/5-thuong-vu-sap-xay-ra-truoc-khi-ky-chuyen-nhuong-Ngoai-hang-Anh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Tottenham ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Sao tr\u1ebb Chirivella chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1eddi Liverpool. </strong>Celtic hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Pedro Chirivella v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 3,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, c\u0169ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y, Rosenborg \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn s\u1edf h\u1eefu sao tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1edbi Liverpool. Nh\u01b0ng Chirivella th\u00ec l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Na Uy ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ecb h\u1ee7y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Arsenal tung chi\u00eau \u0111\u1ed9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu Dembele khi\u1ebfn Barca ng\u00e3 ng\u1eeda.</strong> Trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8, t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery mu\u1ed1n Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ousmane Dembele t\u1eeb Barca. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n mu\u1ed9n Dembele trong v\u00f2ng 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 10 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1ee9 9 c\u1ee7a West Ham \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Arsenal?</strong> Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng West Ham mua Lucas Perez th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb Arsenal \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. Sky Sports kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2116","checkdouble":"193992"},{"date":"08:29 08/08","title":"AC Milan n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua \"bom x\u1ecbt\" Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/20/ac-milan-nang-gia-hoi-mua-bakayoko.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>AC Mian mua Tiemoue Bakayoko c\u1ee7a Chelsea, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n San Siro.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Bakayoko cho AC v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAC Milan \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, sau khi \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Gonzalo Higuain t\u1eeb Juventus, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Siro mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"AC Mian mua Tiemoue Bakayoko b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"AC Mian mua Tiemoue Bakayoko b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/AC-Mian-mua-Tiemoue-Bakayoko-bang-duoc-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Bakayoko v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia quan t\u00e2m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tiemoue Bakayoko c\u1ee7a Chelsea, ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eeba c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o The Blues. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n c\u1ef1u sao Monaco \u0111ang g\u1eb7p \u00e1p l\u1ef1c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, b\u1edfi Chelsea c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAC Milan ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i, song Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 kh\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb. The Blues kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Bakayoko l\u00ean 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/ac-milan-chi-30-trieu-bang-hoi-mua-bakayoko-172-192180.html\" target=\"_blank\">AC Mian mua Tiemoue Bakayoko </span>c\u1ee7a Chelsea, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n San Siro. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tiemoue Bakayoko trong tran Chelsea 1-0 MU chung ket FA Cup 2017/18\" title=\"Tiemoue Bakayoko trong tr\u1eadn Chelsea 1-0 MU chung k\u1ebft FA Cup 2017/18\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/ac-milan-nang-gia-hoi-mua-bakayoko.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>AC Milan n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Tiemoue Bakayoko l\u00ean 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea b\u1ecf ra 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Bakayoko t\u1eeb Monaco, song v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 AC Milan \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Chelsea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb AC Milan, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n sang m\u01b0\u1ee3n. H\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u01b0\u1ee3n ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi mua \u0111\u1ee9t v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAC Milan \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn Anh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Bakayoko ngay trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, AC s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Diadie Samassekou c\u1ee7a Red Bull Salzburg.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2115","checkdouble":"193993"},{"date":"08:43 08/08","title":"Rio Ferdinand lo s\u1ee3 MU s\u1ebd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/6/rio-ferdinand-lo-so-mu-se-that-bai-o-mua-giai-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Rio Ferdinand ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang lo s\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, M.U l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i duy nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u00ean Man City trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf ch\u1eb7ng n\u01b0\u1edbc r\u00fat Man \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee5t h\u01a1i so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0nh nh\u00ecn Man xanh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rio Ferdinand ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Rio Ferdinand ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/rio-ferdinand-lo-so-mu-se-that-bai-o-mua-giai-201819.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 b\u1ee7a v\u00e2y Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi ch\u01b0a b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 b\u1ee7a v\u00e2y \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford. HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi BL\u0110 M.U, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 mua th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 4 \u0111\u1ebfn 5 t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, song \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i M.U m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, trong \u0111\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t Fred \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Man City v\u00e0 Liverpool c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn M.U g\u1eb7p th\u00eam nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mourinho ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean th\u1ee9 3 cho danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Mourinho r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. \u1ede \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Champions League, n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ecf th\u00e0nh Manchester c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Rio Ferdinand lo s\u1ee3 MU s\u1ebd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRio Ferdinand ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang lo s\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rio Ferdinand ha thap nhieu cau thu Barca sau tran thua.\" title=\"Rio Ferdinand h\u1ea1 th\u1ea5p nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Barca sau tr\u1eadn thua.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/4/12/Ferdinand-chi-trich-HLV-Arsene-Wenger-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rio Ferdinand lo s\u1ee3 MU s\u1ebd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u phi\u1ec1n n\u00e3o xung quanh M.U v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. Mourinho r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u01b0ng \u00fd, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 M.U kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 th\u00ec Man City v\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ecf ra \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Man City th\u00ec v\u1eabn v\u1eady, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, c\u00f2n v\u1edbi Liverpool, v\u1edbi g\u1ea7n 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi ra h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch NHA m\u00f9a t\u1edbi&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a M.U, l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t fan h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n M.U gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i s\u1ee3 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2114","checkdouble":"193994"},{"date":"23:43 07/08","title":"HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 ra c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-1 Uzbekistan","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/4/6/hlv-le-thuy-hai-khen-ngoi-1-cau-thu-sau-tran-u23-viet-nam-11-uzbekistan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Uzbekistan, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i khen ng\u1ee3i \u0110\u1ee9c Huy sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a\u00a0U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 7/8, \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 duy\u00ean n\u1ee3 Uzbekistan.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c uy hi\u1ebfp khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, \u0110T U23 Uzbekistan c\u0169ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1ebb g\u00e3y c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ee3t l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau hi\u1ec7p 1 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf ph\u00fat 65 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. R\u1ea5t may Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1eabn k\u1ecbp t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a 1-1 chung cu\u1ed9c.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i khen ng\u1ee3i \u0110\u1ee9c Huysau tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i khen ng\u1ee3i \u0110\u1ee9c Huysau tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/HLV-Le-Thuy-Hai-khen-ngoi-Duc-Huysau-tran-U23-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u1ee9c Huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i khen ng\u1ee3i \u1edf tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-1 U23 Uzbekistan</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng n\u00e0y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Tri th\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb: \"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t r\u1ed3i nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u01a1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea1n. Ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 thu\u1ed1c th\u1eed li\u1ec1u cao c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Park. H\u00f4m nay v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t kh\u00ed h\u1eadu h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 quen r\u1ed3i. Th\u1ee9 2, h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i b\u1eb1ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u00e1p s\u00e1t nhanh, d\u00f9ng s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean l\u00e0m ch\u00fang ta b\u1ecb kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng. Th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t r\u00f5.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ecd c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng, b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh l\u00f9i s\u00e2u, khi ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng l\u00e0 h\u1ecd ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng l\u1ecfng l\u1ebbo. Ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta th\u1ef1c ra kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m nh\u01b0ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u01b0a c\u00f3, c\u00f3 th\u00ec ch\u01b0a gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1\u201d.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tin-moi-nhat-ve-chan-thuong-cua-quang-hai-168-193974.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/tin-moi-nhat-ve-chan-thuong-cua-quang-hai.png\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tin-moi-nhat-ve-chan-thuong-cua-quang-hai-168-193974.html\">Tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 cung c\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin ban \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-u23-uzbekistan-noi-gi-sau-tran-hoa-truoc-u23-viet-nam-168-193970.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/hlv-u23-uzbekistan-noi-gi-sau-tran-hoa-truoc-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-u23-uzbekistan-noi-gi-sau-tran-hoa-truoc-u23-viet-nam-168-193970.html\">HLV U23 Uzbekistan n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV U23 Uzbekistan, Nuraliev Dilshod \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00ec s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 quan \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-phat-bieu-292-193972.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/hlv-park-hang-seo-phat-bieu.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-phat-bieu-292-193972.html\">V\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu, HLV Park Hang Seo lo \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ee7 quan</span><br />\r\nGi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng, HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn lo l\u1eafng khi g\u1eedi l\u1eddi nh\u1eafc r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-168-193967.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-168-193967.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-1 U23 Uzbekistan</span><br />\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 ch\u1ecbu kh\u00f3 di chuy\u1ec3n, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uzbekistan. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n r\u00fat ra...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nong-hlv-park-hang-seo-tao-bat-ngo-lon-tai-danh-sach-chinh-thuc-olympic-viet-nam-168-193960.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/nong-hlv-park-hang-seo-tao-bat-ngo-lon-tai-danh-sach-chinh-thuc-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nong-hlv-park-hang-seo-tao-bat-ngo-lon-tai-danh-sach-chinh-thuc-olympic-viet-nam-168-193960.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: HLV Park Hang Seo lo\u1ea1i V\u0103n L\u00e2m kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br />\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi U23 Uzbekistan, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng H\u1ea3i \u2018l\u01a1\u2019 c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c Huy, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng m\u1eabu m\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201c\u0110\u1ee9c Huy l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 bi\u00ean, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 m\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t. H\u00f4m nay c\u1eadu \u1ea5y chuy\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t hay. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9ng, to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00ec ch\u1ec9 \u0111i c\u00f3 20 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00f4i. V\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o v\u1eafng th\u00ec ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ea5p v\u00e0o. \u0110\u1ee9c Huy l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1ea5y. Em \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng di ASIAD\", \u00f4ng H\u1ea3i n\u00f3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng, b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng l\u00e0 HLV Park Hang Seo li\u00ean t\u1ee5c thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, v\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nhanh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng H\u1ea3i \u2018l\u01a1\u2019 c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ngang c\u01a1 nh\u01b0 Palestine. V\u1ecb c\u1ef1u gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt CLB B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00ec v\u1eady c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u00a0\u1edf ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Highlight U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-1 U23 Uzbekistan<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/7/Highlight-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Uzbekistan.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2113","checkdouble":"193977"},{"date":"00:09 08/08","title":"\u201cTi\u1ebfn D\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/tien-dung-khong-bang-van-lam-nhung-cung-la-thu-mon-tot.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 t\u00ednh to\u00e1n c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Park Hang Seo.</h2><h2>HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i so s\u00e1nh B\u00f9i\u00a0Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u1edbi \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 \u1edf danh s\u00e1ch 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 1 \u1edf \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam hi\u1ec7n nay.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Tien-Dung-khong-bang-Dang-Van-Lam-nhung-cung-la-thu-mon-tot-hinh-anh.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n L\u00e2m chia tay Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec3u l\u00e0 do m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i Olympic ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23, v\u00e0 th\u1ea7y Park \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u01b0u ti\u00ean su\u1ea5t n\u00e0y cho V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i cho bi\u1ebft: \"\u00d4ng \u1ea5y ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p mang 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, mang L\u00e2m th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mang H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng. Khi g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 \u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t th\u00ec c\u00f3 D\u0169ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. \u0110i\u1ec1u g\u00ec c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n h\u1ebft nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 m\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecdn. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7n nh\u00ecn c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ednh to\u00e1n. G\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh th\u00ec H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. N\u00f3i chung ph\u1ea3i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0m sao cho ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt. C\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt h\u1ee3p l\u00fd th\u00ec c\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 h\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 ra con ng\u01b0\u1eddi. HLV n\u00e0o c\u0169ng th\u1ebf\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng H\u1ea3i \"l\u01a1\" c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00e0 \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m.\u00a0Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 \u0110\u00f4ng cho bi\u1ebft: \"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 t\u1ed1t kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0o g\u1ea7n qu\u00e1 th\u00ec th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0o c\u0169ng thua.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta v\u00e0o nhanh qu\u00e1 nh\u01b0 h\u00f4m nay thua l\u00e0 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. D\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00edch, \u00f4ng Park c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft th\u1ebf. V\u00e0 em \u1ea5y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 k\u00e9m d\u00f9 b\u1eaft \u00edt \u1edf V-League. V\u00ec th\u1ebf \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc\".<br />\r\n<strong>Highlight U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan</strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/7/Highlight-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Uzbekistan.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-le-thuy-hai-khen-ngoi-1-cau-thu-sau-tran-u23-viet-nam-11-uzbekistan-168-193977.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/4/6/hlv-le-thuy-hai-khen-ngoi-1-cau-thu-sau-tran-u23-viet-nam-11-uzbekistan.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-le-thuy-hai-khen-ngoi-1-cau-thu-sau-tran-u23-viet-nam-11-uzbekistan-168-193977.html\">HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 ra c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-1 Uzbekistan</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Uzbekistan, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tin-moi-nhat-ve-chan-thuong-cua-quang-hai-168-193974.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/tin-moi-nhat-ve-chan-thuong-cua-quang-hai.png\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tin-moi-nhat-ve-chan-thuong-cua-quang-hai-168-193974.html\">Tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 cung c\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin ban \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-phat-bieu-292-193972.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/hlv-park-hang-seo-phat-bieu.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-phat-bieu-292-193972.html\">V\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu, HLV Park Hang Seo lo \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ee7 quan</span><br />\r\nGi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng, HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn lo l\u1eafng khi g\u1eedi l\u1eddi nh\u1eafc r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-168-193967.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-168-193967.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-1 U23 Uzbekistan</span><br />\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 ch\u1ecbu kh\u00f3 di chuy\u1ec3n, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uzbekistan. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n r\u00fat ra...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p>\r\n<h1>\u00a0</h1></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2112","checkdouble":"193978"},{"date":"00:44 08/08","title":"\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi b\u1ecb g\u1ea1ch t\u00ean kh\u1ecfi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/dang-van-lam-noi-gi-sau-khi-bi-gach-ten-khoi-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kepa Arrizabalaga. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y v\u1edbi Athletic Bilbao.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea kh\u00e1t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nghi ng\u1edd g\u00ec v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c Thibaut Courtois mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi b\u1ecf Chelsea v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1eddi m\u1eddi ch\u00e0o t\u1eeb Real Madrid, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ra \u0111i. T\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi Real b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh, anh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u00e3 2 ng\u00e0y tr\u00f4i qua k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb h\u1ea1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, Courtois v\u1eabn b\u1eb7t v\u00f4 \u00e2m t\u00edn. K\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m r\u00f5 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a HLV Maurizio Sarri c\u0169ng b\u1ecb h\u1ee7y b\u1ecf. Th\u00f4ng qua \u0111\u00f3, Courtois g\u1eedi \u0111i th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00eam b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o cho Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kepa Arrizabalaga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kepa Arrizabalaga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/15/Chelsea-dong-y-chi-71-trieu-bang-mua-Kepa-Arrizabalaga-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Courtois kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n thi\u1ebft tha \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Courtois b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c ra tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m r\u00f5 v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n duy tr\u00ec k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt trong \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng dung t\u00fang h\u00e0nh vi n\u00e0y. Song song v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, The Blues c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u00ecm th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nCh\u1ed1t mua Kepa</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 t\u1edd Telegraph m\u1edbi \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kepa Arrizabalaga c\u1ee7a Athletic Bilbao. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Bilbao tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o cho th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 24 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi The Blues bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a anh n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp di\u1ec5n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kepa Arrizabalaga\" title=\"Kepa Arrizabalaga\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/chelsea-dong-y-chi-71-trieu-bang-mua-kepa-arrizabalaga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Kepa Arrizabalaga</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y Chelsea s\u1eafp ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a CLB ch\u1ec9 sau 1 n\u0103m khi \u0111\u01b0a Alvaro Morata v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ea3 ngay 58 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng l\u00ean 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u00f9y th\u00e0nh t\u00edch. N\u00f3 c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0a Kepa tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 1 th\u00e1ng sau khi Liverpool chi 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Alisson t\u1eeb Roma.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00fac n\u00e0y, Chelsea \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Kepa. Song song v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng k\u1ef3 k\u00e8o Real gia t\u0103ng th\u00eam s\u1ee9c n\u1eb7ng trong \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb mua Courtois. Los Blancos ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n chi 31 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (35 tri\u1ec7u Euro) trong khi CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sevilla-muon-co-batshuayi-180-193959.html\">\u201cBom x\u1ecbt\u201d Chelsea s\u1eafp chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi La Liga thi \u0111\u1ea5u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-muon-kovacic-172-193958.html\">L\u1ed9 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a Mateo Kovacic \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-chelsea-hy-vong-sarri-khong-kho-hieu-nhu-conte-172-193918.html\">Sao Chelsea hy v\u1ecdng Sarri kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u nh\u01b0 Conte</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-cho-nantes-muon-matt-miazga-172-193916.html\">Sao tr\u1ebb Chelsea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barkley-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-chelsea-172-193912.html\">\u201cSao x\u1ecbt\u201d Chelsea hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1eddi d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2111","checkdouble":"193979"},{"date":"00:56 08/08","title":"Chuy\u00ean gia Vi\u1ec7t n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uzbekistan?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/chuyen-gia-viet-noi-gi-ve-tran-hoa-cua-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-truoc-uzbekistan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nguy\u1ec5n S\u1ef9 Hi\u1ec3n cho r\u1eb1ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n r\u00fat kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Uzbekistan.</h2><h2>Chuy\u00ean gia Nguy\u1ec5n S\u1ef9 Hi\u1ec3n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u00ean gia Nguy\u1ec5n S\u1ef9 Hi\u1ec3n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u00ean gia Nguy\u1ec5n S\u1ef9 Hi\u1ec3n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/38693374-407003336372383-80023-8216-9368-1533647643_600x0.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam su\u00fdt b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai tr\u01b0\u1edbc\u00a0Uzbekistan</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 7/8, \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Uzbekistan v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n S\u1ef9 Hi\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cKh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t b\u1ed5 \u00edch cho U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam\". <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i th\u1ea5y h\u00f4m nay \u0110\u1ee9c Huy \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 bi\u00ean, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u00fang ta m\u1ea5t ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng, ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o l\u00fac \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, U23 Uzbekistan ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t khi ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c,d\u00f9 h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u BHL c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i r\u00fat kinh nghi\u1ec7m.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb c\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng c\u00f3 l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i cho pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c. \u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft khi ng\u00f4i sao SLNA \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee1 b\u00f3ng b\u1eb1ng ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u0103ng b\u00f3ng b\u1eb1ng ch\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00fa h\u00edch \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo th\u00eam t\u1ef1 tin b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ASIAD. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Olympic Pakistan, Nepal v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2110","checkdouble":"193980"},{"date":"01:04 08/08","title":"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vui h\u1ebft n\u1ea5c khi n\u00e2ng c\u00fap, th\u1ea7y Park l\u1eb7ng l\u1ebd m\u1ed9t g\u00f3c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/nhung-hinh-anh-an-tuo