ble":"193987"},{"date":"06:28 08/08","title":"Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng cho M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/3/tottenham-da-dong-y-ban-trung-ve-khung-cho-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Toby Alderweireld cho M.U. Tuy nhi\u00ean, CLB B\u1eafc London \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y cho t\u1edbi khi h\u1ecd t\u00ecm ra ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham ch\u1ea5p thu\u1eadn nh\u1ea3 Alderweireld cho M.U</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a M.U. \u00d4ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ea5p tr\u00ean mang v\u1ec1 1 trong 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean (ho\u1eb7c c\u1ea3 hai) Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham v\u00e0 Harry Maguire.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7t l\u00ean b\u00e0n c\u00e2n, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alderweireld l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 thi h\u01a1n v\u1edbi M.U. X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi CLB, anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Maguire v\u1edbi Leicester City. C\u0169ng v\u00ec th\u1ebf, Leicester quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t ra \u0111i b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c n\u1eb7ng t\u1eeb M.U.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Toby Alderweireld cho MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Toby Alderweireld cho MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/3/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-hom-nay-ngay-48,-tin-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Toby Alderweireld cho M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Toby Alderweireld cho M.U v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 m\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sau khi theo \u0111u\u1ed5i trung v\u1ec7 29 tu\u1ed5i trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Tottenham</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng Tottenham kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1ea1i Alderweireld cho M.U ngay b\u00e2y gi\u1edd. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 mang v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf cho tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pochettino\" title=\"HLV Pochettino\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/Mauricio-Pochettino-noi-ve-chuyen-nhuong-Tottenham-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Pochettino ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u00eam t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, Tottenham v\u1eabn \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c mua s\u1eafm. H\u1ecd nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u00e1i t\u00ean nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai v\u1ec1. S\u1ef1 ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p trong tuy\u1ec3n m\u1ed9 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Spurs l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u M.U l\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1edbc. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n B n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Alderweireld.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, t\u1eeb gi\u1edd t\u1edbi khi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00eam th\u1ee9 5 (9/8), M.U s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng mang v\u1ec1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 trung v\u1ec7. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0 Alderweireld, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd li\u00ean h\u1ec7 g\u1ea5p v\u1edbi Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barcelona hay Jerome Boateng c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 Maguire v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u1eb7ng \u0111\u00f4.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 Alderweireld hay b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0o \u1edf tr\u00ean gia nh\u1eadp, M.U c\u0169ng chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i Marcos Rojo. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina n\u1eb1m trong danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7n tinh gi\u1ea3n bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf m\u00e0 HLV Mourinho tr\u00ecnh l\u00ean l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/quan-diem-mu-nen-mua-zaha-172-193931.html\">Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: M.U n\u00ean g\u1ea1t b\u1ecf s\u0129 di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 mua l\u1ea1i Wilfried Zaha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-dau-hieu-cuc-lon-cho-thay-mu-chuan-bi-don-trung-ve-moi-172-193882.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn cho th\u1ea5y M.U chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n trung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-pogba-da-tro-lai-man-united-172-193880.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Pogba \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Man United</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/willian-chinh-thuc-dua-ra-cau-tra-loi-cho-mu-barca-172-193877.html\">Willian ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho M.U, Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-boateng-voi-mu-172-193871.html\">Arsenal gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh sao tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/willian-mot-lan-nua-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-172-193826.html\">Willian: T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn MU ho\u1eb7c Real n\u1ebfu...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2105","checkdouble":"193988"},{"date":"06:49 08/08","title":"2 \u201ch\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u201d ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda r\u1eddi Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/12/2-hang-thai-tien-gan-toi-canh-cua-roi-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arsenal s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i Lucas Perez v\u00e0 David Ospina. Trong khi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ebfn West Ham ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf th\u00ec th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Besiktas.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Perez s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ebfn West Ham</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lucas Perez t\u1eeb Deportivo. Khi \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd m\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Jamie Vardy v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt l\u00e0 Perez \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1. Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh gi\u00e0u th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng trong t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng \u0111u\u1ed1i s\u1ee9c. \u0110\u1ebfn m\u00f9a 2017/18, Perez b\u1ecb Arsenal \u0111\u1ea9y tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Deportivo d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Alexandre Lacazette.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i Lucas Perez v\u00e0 David Ospina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Arsenal s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i Lucas Perez v\u00e0 David Ospina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/12/ban-hop-dong-thu-9-cua-west-ham-den-tu-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Arsenal s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i Lucas Perez v\u00e0 David Ospina</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSang m\u00f9a m\u1edbi 2018/19, Perez ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Arsenal. Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cho m\u00ecnh nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00e1c \u1edf hai c\u00e1nh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7n thanh l\u00fd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb West Ham, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd, ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7 8 tri\u1ec7u t\u1eeb Perez sau 2 n\u0103m. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ebfn ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i West Ham v\u00e0 s\u1edbm ra m\u1eaft CLB n\u00e0y. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Ospina\" title=\"thu mon Ospina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/2/15/hlv-wenger-xac-nhan-thu-mon-bat-chinh-truoc-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ospina \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Besiktas</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nOspina \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Besiktas</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 Lucas Perez, David Ospina kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec &ldquo;ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eeba&rdquo; c\u1ee7a Arsenal trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c mang v\u1ec1 Bernd Leno t\u1eeb Bayer Leverkusen c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n Petr Cech, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u1ea7n th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia d\u00f9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u00f3ng b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Ospina chia tay Arsenal h\u00e8 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, anh \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Besiktas v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 \u0111ang c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n m\u1edbi thay th\u1ebf Tolga Zengin s\u1eafp sang tu\u1ed5i 35. Ospina tr\u1ebb h\u01a1n 4 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u cho Besiktas.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-gia-nhap-cuoc-dua-gianh-boateng-voi-mu-172-193871.html\">Arsenal gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh sao tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-bao-tin-buon-cho-arsenal-vu-dembele-180-193861.html\">Barca b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho Arsenal v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n 105 tri\u1ec7u euro</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/xac-nhan-arsenal-va-chelsea-quan-tam-leon-bailey-172-193859.html\">X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn: Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea quan t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng hot Bundesliga</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-nham-sao-thuy-sy-thay-nacho-monreal-172-193853.html\">Arsenal nh\u1eafm sao Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 thay Nacho Monreal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/aaron-ramsey-phu-nhan-voi-vinh-arsenal-bang-luong-khung-172-193837.html\">Aaron Ramsey ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn v\u00f2i v\u0129nh Arsenal b\u1eb1ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2104","checkdouble":"193989"},{"date":"15:22 07/08","title":"S\u1ed1 4 v\u00e0 c\u01a1n \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/so-4-va-con-dau-dau-cua-thay-park.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo lu\u1eadt ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i ASIAD, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i U23. V\u00e0 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i lo\u1ea1i ai trong s\u1ed1 4 c\u1ef1u binh c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-tran-dau-ngay-hom-nay-78-372-193948.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-tran-dau-ngay-hom-nay-78.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-tran-dau-ngay-hom-nay-78-372-193948.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan 19h30 ng\u00e0y 7/8 (U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018)</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u01a1n \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi lu\u00f4n e ng\u1ea1i con s\u1ed1 4 b\u1edfi theo quan ni\u1ec7m ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0110\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 t\u1eed. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y Park, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u00f4ng c\u0169ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u khi s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 ai v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 4 trong 4 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23 l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a 4 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean tu\u1ed5i 23 \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"S\u1ed1 4 v\u00e0 c\u01a1n \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"S\u1ed1 4 v\u00e0 c\u01a1n \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/hlv-park-hang-seo-gui-loi-nhan-toi-nguoi-ham-mo-bong-da-viet-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i g\u1ea1ch t\u00ean m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23 khi ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed1i nay, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi U23 Uzbekistan, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn ra nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng HLV Park Hang Seo tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u00e1p l\u1ef1c c\u1ea1nh tranh l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang r\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1edfi h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 &lsquo;ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m&rsquo; trong m\u1eaft \u00f4ng Park. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb m\u00e0, nh\u1eefng &lsquo;l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng&rsquo; c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh V\u0103n L\u00e2m \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u00ec c\u1ea3 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u1edf l\u1ea1i. V\u00e0 v\u00ec th\u1ebf, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi v\u1edbi Uzbekistan \u0111\u1ec3 qua \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-viet-nam-vo-dich-vinaphone-cup-loi-khang-dinh-cua-thay-park-168-193817.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/u23-viet-nam-vo-dich-vinaphone-cup-loi-khang-dinh-cua-thay-park.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-viet-nam-vo-dich-vinaphone-cup-loi-khang-dinh-cua-thay-park-168-193817.html\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf: L\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park</span><br>\r\nTh\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong ngh\u1ec1 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi gi\u00fap  U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Vinaphone Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110i t\u00ecm s\u1ed1 4<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t n\u0103m c\u00f3 4 m\u00f9a xu\u00e2n, h\u1ea1, thu, \u0111\u00f4ng th\u00ec trong tay HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 4 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c b\u1ed5 sung v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u00f9a \u0110\u00f4ng lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1ebfn sau c\u00f9ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1nh l\u1ebdo, t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 th\u00ec ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n 4 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Park c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mong mu\u1ed1n m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd r\u01a1i v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 4, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u1edf nh\u00e0 xem ASIAD. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean quy \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1eabn l\u00e0 quy \u0111\u1ecbnh, v\u00e0 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn lu\u1eadt ch\u01a1i chung l\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23 khi tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Park Hang Seo t\u1eebng n\u00f3i s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng 3 'c\u1ef1u binh' \u1edf ASIAD 2018, v\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u1eabn \u0111ang chia \u0111\u1ec1u cho c\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Anh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 hai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00e0 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Viet Nam\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/vq-01-1640.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Li\u1ec7u V\u0103n L\u00e2m, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft s\u1ebd l\u00e0 3 'c\u1ef1u binh' tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh \u0110\u1ee9c d\u00f9 l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 1 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0ng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i cho anh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 33, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Anh \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 nhanh nh\u1eb9n nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Do \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn ho\u1eb7c d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd b\u1ecb thay th\u1ebf b\u1edfi c\u00e1c trung phong tr\u1ebb trung kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh hay Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft d\u00f9 n\u1eafm gi\u1eef t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Uzbekistan, anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eabn b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u00edt nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi khen t\u1eeb c\u1ea3 hai HLV U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Palestine, tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n sai v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Quy\u1ebft &lsquo;c\u00f2i&rsquo; l\u1ea1i v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-19h30-ngay-078-doi-no-duoc-khong-168-193900.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-19h30-ngay-078-doi-no-duoc-khong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-19h30-ngay-078-doi-no-duoc-khong-168-193900.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan (19h30 ng\u00e0y 07/8): \u0110\u00f2i n\u1ee3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng?</span><br>\r\nU23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f2i n\u1ee3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Uzbekistan sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018. V\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111ang c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u1edf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, d\u00f9 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn sau nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm hy v\u1ecdng tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i. Vi\u1ec7c \u00f4ng Park s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 gi\u1eef 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i d\u00f9 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a anh \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1ng khen ng\u1ee3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Oman. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed anh c\u00f2n su\u00fdt n\u1eefa \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean m\u00ecnh l\u00ean b\u1ea3ng \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed n\u1ebfu th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a anh \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 82.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Do Hung Dung\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/tien-ve-hung-dung-lo-lang-ve-kha-nang-du-asiad.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 th\u00ec D\u0169ng &lsquo;ch\u00edp&rsquo; kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c '\u0111\u00e0n em' U23, trong khi kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1eb1ng V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c hay V\u0103n L\u00e2m, n\u00ean n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 anh b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i t\u00f3m l\u1ea1i, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u tay 3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1eafng, b\u1ea1i. Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra s\u1ed1 4 m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh \u0111ang c\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Highlight Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Palestine<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/3/Highlight-Viet-Nam-vs-Palestine-.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/danh-sach-chinh-thuc-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-ai-se-bi-loai-168-193940.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/danh-sach-chinh-thuc-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-ai-se-bi-loai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/danh-sach-chinh-thuc-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-ai-se-bi-loai-168-193940.html\">Danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD: Ai s\u1ebd b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i?</span><br>\r\nSau khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Uzbekistan k\u1ebft th\u00fac, HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u ai s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/lo-dien-doi-hinh-ra-san-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-168-193938.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/lo-dien-doi-hinh-ra-san-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/lo-dien-doi-hinh-ra-san-tran-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-uzbekistan-168-193938.html\">L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan</span><br>\r\nTheo ngu\u1ed3n tin th\u00e2n c\u1eadn, g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd tung ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Uzbekistan v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay 7/8.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2103","checkdouble":"193944"}]}